# Do NOT ignore the keystore — it is intentionally included so the CI/CD
# chain can build and sign APKs from this repo. Store this repo private.
# If you move to a public repo, remove the keystore and manage it via
# CI secrets (ANDROID_KEYSTORE base64, ANDROID_KEY_ALIAS, ANDROID_STORE_PASSWORD).
